{
  "stem": "14002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This Anton want to take off the earrings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He couldn't open them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he tore them down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is what that crying was all about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Of course, we were so in a-- in a daze, we couldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We couldn't believe that a thing like that would happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That we know the guy for so many years, that he would do a thing like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The next day, they took us to the next town, Neresnytsya.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were there a couple days in the shul, in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Of course, there was no food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody gave us any food or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we didn't even think about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "See, down there, it was a-- it was a small-- it was not the normal train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was a smaller version of a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Even the tracks were not as wide as the normal train is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us in an open car, in an open wagon, not-- not closed or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are-- the-- it didn't took long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just had to go, I would say, about 20 kilometers, to the town of Teresva, or Teresva, how they used to call it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Down there, the bigger, the normal car-- the normal train used to go from there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we were riding, we realized that we are-- we are riding more to inland of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came to a station by the name of Mateszalka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the name of that town in-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As we came down from the station, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were-- we were in open field for about two days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they took us in-- in town, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
